### Create student
POST http://localhost:8080/api/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1995-05-20",
  "phone": "11999999999",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 123",
  "planId": 1,
  "active": true
}

###

### List all students
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search by name (accent/case insensitive)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students?name=joao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by payment status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students?paymentStatus=A receber
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by age range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students?minAge=18&maxAge=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by active status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get student by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update student
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/students/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1995-05-20",
  "phone": "11988888888",
  "email": "joao.novo@example.com",
  "address": "Rua Nova, 456",
  "planId": 1,
  "active": true
}

###

### Delete student
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/students/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get student subscriptions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/1/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
